    <div class="cta-content reveal">
      <img src="/images/wade_wave.png" alt="Wade waving" class="cta-duck" />
      <h2 class="cta-title font-display">Ready to Waddle?</h2>
      <p class="cta-subtitle">
        Start tracking your hydration today. Collect ducks, complete challenges, and build the healthiest streak of your life.
